structure_explanation.S35,S13: Key format: 'enabledParam,compareToKey' where S35 is enabled parameter and S13 is comparison key
structure_explanation.baseline:value: Reference measurement value to compare against
structure_explanation.info: Position indicator: '+' (all above), '-' (all below), or 'b#' (# variations below baseline)
structure_explanation.data:keys: Numerical measurement points using actual modified values
structure_explanation.data:values: Actual measurements. Must be initially null/empty when created by sense_config_base.py
